What is the result when you run this:
```
using FastRationals

n = 10_000
qs = [Rational{BigInt}(1,i) for i=1:n];
fastqs = [FastQBig(1,i) for i=1:n];
qs_time = @belapsed sum($qs);
fastqs_time = @belapsed sum($fastqs);
round(qs_time / fastqs_time, digits=2)
```

